'From Squeak 2.2beta of Sept 16, 1998 on 20 September 1998 at 1:14:36 pm'!"Change Set:		ResortOrganizationsDate:			20 September 1998Author:			Dan IngallsRemoves all empty categories, and resorts the category arrays using case-insensitive comparisons (some were still sorted on ascii code from before we changed this)."!"Postscript:Resort all organizations in the system (takes a while)."Smalltalk allBehaviorsDo:	[:c | c organization removeEmptyCategories.	c organization changeFromString: c organization printString].SystemOrganization removeEmptyCategories.SystemOrganization changeFromString: SystemOrganization printString.!